CNX Gas Company LLC requests approval to modify its Permit 
#2934-02, U12A, BU-0875 to add two (2) two inch drip lines as shown on the attached exhibit 1A. The first drip which runs from the U12A 12" pipeline will require approximately 330' of 2" pipeline with a disturbance of .57 acres. This line runs the 12" line to a drip valve on the S12-258 location. The second proposed drip line will require approximately 785' of 2" water line with a disturbance of 1.35 acres. this line runs from the 12" pipeline to a tank located on Vance Fork.
